Dayo Amusa is a Known name in the Yoruba Nollywood Industry, She has carved a niche for herself in the Theatre Industry and recently she launch her music career with some singles that enjoyed airwaves.

The theatre diva received some backlash from her fans recently after she wrote on her Instagram page about how she enjoys having S*x.

This didn’t go down well with some of her fans but to some, it’s an opportunity of making their intentions known.

A fan with a restricted account @phlexypeter on Instagram sent a DM to @dayoamusa requesting for a one night stand.

The message wasn’t acceptable for for Dayo amusa as she replied the fan with a dirty response.





			
